《神佑擂台》2008年11月时在[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]上21个媒体的汇总得分为75%<ref>{{cite web | title=Ehrgeiz Reviews | url=http://www.gamerankings.com/ps/197216-ehrgeiz/index.html | work=GameRankings.com | accessdate=2008-11-15 | archive-date=2019-04-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190429061856/https://www.gamerankings.com/ps/197216-ehrgeiz/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

